## Key Functions

### Game Loop (Main.bb)
```blitzbasic
Function Main()
    ; Check dependencies
    ; Load configs
    ; Initialize graphics
    ; Load assets
    ; Enter game loop
End Function

Function GameLoop()
    UpdatePlayerInput()
    UpdateNPCs()
    UpdateEvents()
    UpdatePhysics()
    RenderScene()
    UpdateUI()
End Function
```

### NPC System (NPCs.bb)
```blitzbasic
Function CreateNPC%(type%)
    npc.NPCs = New NPCs
    npc\NPCtype = type
    npc\obj = LoadMesh("npcs/" + NPCFilename$(type))
    npc\State = 0  ; Idle state
    Return Handle(npc)
End Function

Function UpdateNPCs()
    For npc.NPCs = Each NPCs
        Select npc\NPCtype
            Case NPC_SCP_173: UpdateSCP173(npc)
            Case NPC_SCP_096: UpdateSCP096(npc)
            Case NPC_SCP_106: UpdateSCP106(npc)
            ; ...
        End Select
    Next
End Function
```

### Save System (Save.bb)
```blitzbasic
Function SaveGame(slot%)
    file = WriteFile("save" + slot + ".sav")
    ; Write player state
    WriteInt(file, Health)
    WriteInt(file, PlayerRoom)
    WriteInt(file, Stamina)
    ; Write inventory
    ; Write NPC states
    ; Write events
    CloseFile(file)
End Function

Function LoadGame(slot%)
    file = ReadFile("save" + slot + ".sav")
    ; Read and restore state
    CloseFile(file)
End Function
```

### Map Generation (MapSystem.bb)
```blitzbasic
Function GenerateMap()
    ; Clear existing rooms
    ; Place starting room
    ; Loop: place rooms based on connectivity
    ;   - Check commonness
    ;   - Verify zone rules
    ;   - Check door compatibility
    ; Place doors and connections
    ; Generate forest if applicable
End Function
```

## Coding Conventions

### Naming
```blitzbasic
; Functions: PascalCase
Function CreateNPC()
Function UpdateEvents()
Function LoadMaterials()

; Variables: camelCase with type suffix
Local playerObj%
Local speed#
Local name$

; Constants: UPPER_CASE or Prefix
Const MAX_HEALTH = 100
Const ZONE_LCZ = 0
```

### Error Handling
```blitzbasic
; Safe loading pattern (StrictLoads.bb)
Function StrictLoadMesh$(file$)
    If FileType(file) = 0 Then
        RuntimeError("Missing file: " + file)
    End If
    Return LoadMesh(file)
End Function

; Error tracking
Global CatchErrors%[100]
Global ErrorCount%
```

### State Machines
```blitzbasic
; NPC state machine pattern
Select npc\State
    Case STATE_IDLE
        ; Check for player detection
        ; Wander behavior
    Case STATE_CHASE
        ; Move toward player
        ; Attack if close
    Case STATE_ATTACK
        ; Execute attack
        ; Return to chase
    Case STATE_FLEE
        ; Move away from player
End Select
```

## WASM Port Notes

### Virtualization Layer
The WASM port requires virtualizing Windows API calls:

```blitzbasic
; Original Windows API call
kernel32_decls:
Function GetTickCount%() ...

; Virtualized for WASM
; Need implementations in runtime.js
```

### Memory Banks
SCPCB uses memory banks extensively - see `spec_memory_banks.md`:

```blitzbasic
; Data collection for save system
collectDataStatements()
```

### Critical DLL Dependencies

| DLL | Purpose | WASM Replacement |
|-----|---------|------------------|
| fmod.dll | Audio | Web Audio API |
| zlibwapi.dll | ZIP access | JSZip |
| FreeImage.dll | Image loading | Canvas/Image |
| BlitzMovie.dll | Video | HTML5 Video |
| kernel32.dll | Windows API | JavaScript |

## Common Patterns

### Game Loop Pattern
```blitzbasic
While Not AppTerminate
    ; Update phase
    UpdatePlayer()
    UpdateNPCs()
    UpdateEvents()

    ; Render phase
    ClearWorld True, True, True
    RenderWorld

    ; Frame limiting
    Flip(1)
Wend
End
```

### Player Detection Pattern
```blitzbasic
Function CanSeePlayer%(npc)
    ; Check line of sight
    ; Check distance
    ; Check angle
    ; Check obstacles
    Return result%
End Function

Function CanHearPlayer%(npc)
    ; Check distance
    ; Check obstacles
    ; Check movement noise
    Return result%
End Function
```

### Room Transition Pattern
```blitzbasic
Function ChangeRoom%(room_id%, door%)
    ; Save current room state
    SaveRoomState()

    ; Load new room
    PlayerRoom = room_id
    LoadRoom(room_id)

    ; Position player
    PositionEntity Collider, DoorX(door), DoorY(door), DoorZ(door)

    ; Trigger events
    TriggerRoomEvents(room_id)
End Function
```

